title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“East Coast's leading snake-cake and pie company is now entering greater L.A.” [From a classified ad in the Los Angeles Times, September 22, 1983. Submitted by Julian Ross, Los Angeles.]
